<note n="0507008" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0507008">佛【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0507009" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0507009">長跪叉手【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note>
